\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {28}{\ignorespaces Ranking of kinematic variables by their individual signal-vs-background separation power, quantified by the ROC AUC. The top variables (\(\mittau _\mathrm {h}\) \(p_\mathrm {T}\), \(m_\mathrm {vis}\), \(N_\mathrm {jets}\), \(E_\mathrm {T}^\mathrm {miss}\)) all have AUC \textgreater {} 0.63, while pseudorapidity variables show minimal discrimination (AUC near 0.5). The NN combines all 14 variables to achieve a test AUC of 0.825.\relax }}{30}{figure.caption.62}\protected@file@percent }
